{"tid":1910870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7起，勞工界同特首選舉我要有SAY!","createTime":"2020-03-05T03:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T00:12:14.000Z","uid":242262,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d1317ca3adf26a0a61bc06d6268d263953d69887","tid":1910870,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:29:10.000Z","msg":"廢話唔講，上星期第一次試用7起組隊<br />\n今日已經交左表俾職工會登記<br />\n唔敢講最後結果係點，但唔做就一定輸<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://7up.hkpetitions.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F7up.hkpetitions.com&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=f038e2d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://7up.hkpetitions.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cskU5Qn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcskU5Qn.jpg&h=dc8719c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DG3Xdcm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDG3Xdcm.jpg&h=9a932f55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://Hkpetitions.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHkpetitions.com&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=2e72b91a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Hkpetitions.com</a> 團隊最新推出<br />\n7起：起工會神器，不但加速組隊進度，還提供 會章Generator 及已成立工會會章範本 幫助大家提升處理文件效率，最後大家向職登局交上表格和工作證明文件，就完成申請。<br />\n重奪公民權利 保障工人權益<br />\n<a href=\"https://7up.hkpetitions.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F7up.hkpetitions.com&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=f038e2d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://7up.hkpetitions.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hNlNZpVmew5kUPsGd5TNHzUaRL_fGaUR84Y8n7VbeiY/edit?usp=drivesdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1hNlNZpVmew5kUPsGd5TNHzUaRL_fGaUR84Y8n7VbeiY%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Ddrivesdk&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=be5806f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hNlNZpVmew5kUPsGd5TNHzUaRL_fGaUR84Y8n7VbeiY/edit?usp=drivesdk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每個香港人都可以拎三票<br />\n1. 地區個人票<br />\n（立法會地方選區有得投）<br />\n2. 功能組別個人票 (正常人係超級區議會，特定人士係特別界別）<br />\n3. 功能組別團體票(不可跟2同一界別)<br />\n<br />\n呢個群組鼓勵大家轉功能組別和<br />\n組工會拎第三票！（勞工界）<br />\n<br />\n📌如何成立社團？<br />\n1. 齊集三人，須有相關文化資歷證明<br />\n2. 準備社團資料 - 宗旨/ 規章/ 已或擬舉辦的活動<br />\n3. 準備個人資料 - 身分證副本/ 住址+會址證明 (3個月內)(銀行/水電煤單據)<br />\n4. 組員互簽名，互交換文件<br />\n5. 寄出去 /親身交到警總 Done!<br />\n<br />\n(1)成立7人工會懶人包<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1QIIjjz-krTtp9TLqLy3Zjt9eGN8kdCjZ?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1QIIjjz-krTtp9TLqLy3Zjt9eGN8kdCjZ%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=28c0691d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1QIIjjz-krTtp9TLqLy3Zjt9eGN8kdCjZ?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會功能組別攻略總公海<br />\n【功能組別終極整合】<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_57.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fblog-post_57.html%3Fm%3D1&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=a642e1b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_57.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/legcodiscuss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flegcodiscuss&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=7fc17459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/legcodiscuss</a>"},{"pid":"49481770aaf3d1e3c0388ad9719e9fa72ab412f8","tid":1910870,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:32:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10a64c570df47c48ba96777a644b7ce442fd8acf","tid":1910870,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\